88
00:08:02,315 --> 00:08:03,900
Somos todos pecadores.

89
00:08:03,983 --> 00:08:05,693
Amém.

90
00:08:06,486 --> 00:08:09,238
Mas, continuando a fazer o que fazemos,

91
00:08:09,906 --> 00:08:13,618
